metadata.description:
MSQS reveal the duality of human nature, a pure vision of human soul, the evil and the good. 
how deep can we sin? how high can we fly? 
allure. repulse. create. destroy. love. hate. give. take.

Ocean pollution NFT 10% profit goes to Bahamas Plastic Movement organization. All the donations are posted in the official WINDJAMMERS social media accounts.

We stand for unity, love and peace.
